WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.609 --> 00:00:03.810
Let's take a selfie!

2
00:00:03.810 --> 00:00:06.610
Oh, that's a good idea. We've never taken a selfie.

3
00:00:06.610 --> 00:00:07.700
You want to take it?

4
00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:08.699
Yep.

5
00:00:08.699 --> 00:00:22.219
Okay.

6
00:00:22.219 --> 00:00:24.219
I'm sorry. I couldn't protect you back then.

7
00:00:24.219 --> 00:00:29.239
But I have to let go of the past and forgive myself.

8
00:00:29.239 --> 00:00:31.620
What?

9
00:00:31.620 --> 00:00:38.420
What's the matter? Why are you crying?

10
00:00:38.420 --> 00:00:42.759
I'm just... I'm so happy.

11
00:00:42.759 --> 00:00:48.350
This marriage is the most wonderful thing.

12
00:00:48.350 --> 00:00:51.950
Marry and you have to be wonderful.

13
00:00:51.950 --> 00:00:53.399
What's this?

14
00:00:53.399 --> 00:00:56.619
I bought these for you.

15
00:00:57.619 --> 00:00:58.619
Eat them!

16
00:00:58.619 --> 00:01:00.009
What?

17
00:01:00.009 --> 00:01:02.009
These are eternal flowers.

18
00:01:02.009 --> 00:01:06.010
As long as you take care of them, they will never wilt.

19
00:01:06.010 --> 00:01:08.010
I mean, how romantic is that?

20
00:01:10.010 --> 00:01:14.150
Why do you keep spending so much money?

